videos.headline: Memphis opens game with 94-yard kickoff-return TD
videos.description: Chris Claybrooks fields the opening kickoff for Memphis and takes it the other way 94 yards for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Memphis opens game with 94-yard kickoff-return TD 2019/11/29

videos.headline: Cinci player flops in tussle
videos.description: Memphis' Joey Magnifico and Cincinnati's Perry Young get into a tussle, with Young flopping after the ordeal. Both would receive offsetting penalties.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cinci player flops in tussle) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jones battles to cross goal line for Memphis TD
videos.description: Brady White throws over the middle to Kedarian Jones, who fights his way into the end zone for a Memphis touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jones battles to cross goal line for Memphis TD) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cinci uses pick route for short TD
videos.description: Ben Bryant throws the ball to a crossing Leonard Taylor who hits pay dirt for a four-yard Cincinnati score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cinci uses pick route for short TD) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Warren caps off 14-play drive with TD
videos.description: Michael Warren II fights through the pile for a 3-yard touchdown to even the score at 17-17.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Warren caps off 14-play drive with TD) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Coxie comes up with 46-yard TD grab
videos.description: Damonte Coxie reels in the 46-yard touchdown throw as Memphis extends its lead over Cincinnati.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Coxie comes up with 46-yard TD grab) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bryant calls his own number for Cinci TD
videos.description: Ben Bryant keep the ball himself and runs 12 yards into the end zone for a Cincinnati touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bryant calls his own number for Cinci TD) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Memphis' Gibson cuts back into open space for late TD
videos.description: Antonio Gibson takes the handoff and cuts back into open space and runs into the end zone for a 29-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Memphis' Gibson cuts back into open space for late TD) 2019/11/29 ESHEET
